    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We know without desire living is not possible.  &lt;br&gt;
It amazes me the way  &lt;br&gt;
the concept of desirelessness  &lt;br&gt;
has been taught and understood in our society.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We know a desire and dreams  &lt;br&gt;
helps human moving in his life  &lt;br&gt;
With desire human eat, drink and walk,  &lt;br&gt;
With desire human talk, dance and sing,  &lt;br&gt;
With desire human search, paint, and construct.  &lt;br&gt;
With the desire, we want to live and die!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
